    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Areas of low-lying land reclaimed from the sea, a river, or other body of water, and enclosed by dikes. For a piece of marshy or boggy land, use "marshes."</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
